==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
{{ARchar|'''ذ '''/''' ‍ذ'''}} (ðāl)

# The ninth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[د]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ر]]}}.
# The twenty-fifth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[خ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ض]]}}.

